title: [FSX/P3D] Ants Airplanes Drifter Ultralight v1.10
description:
Ant's Airplanes Drifter Ultralight v1.10 for you guys.

Remove the old shortcuts from your Start menu BEFORE installing this to prevent duplicate shortcuts. As far as I know this can be installed on top of the old version, but a clean install is RECOMMENDED as always.

This, IMHO, is still the best ultralight for FSX/P3D despite being released years ago. Support Anthony by buying his products whenever you can.

Enjoy!
